snippet.title: The Cabin Factory | Release Date Reveal Trailer (Steam PC)
snippet.description:
The Cabin Factory releasing on PC via Steam December 13th 2024! 
Your job at the Cabin Factory is simple: inspect a series of cabins, and decide on whether they’re safe or not. If you do find any anomalies, get out…immediately.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3311740/The_Cabin_Factory
Twitter: https://x.com/ICS_indie
Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@UCM8hUffCqZSShTLJ7e75-Lg 

Trailer editor: Owen Trett
